init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: What kind of person will you be?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In the movie you see yourself walking around a big city, and then sitting down in front of a computer.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You notice that you are able to control what happens in the movie, and you start manipulating things for your own amusement.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: does a hypnosis session, and the former you remembers everything.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are told it is possible, but difficult.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They go back into hypnosis, and you are brought back to life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are eager to see what you have been missing, but the whole process has exhausted you.
